data.description: NO HOA or CDD Charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home perfect for the first time home buyer or investors! This home is in a desirable area, centrally located convenient to shopping, downtown, I75 and only 10 minutes away from the amazing Siesta Key beach. The kitchen looks out to the living room and dining room allowing for entertaining, or family gatherings. Great backyard with more than enough space for a family or outdoor dining. Just minutes away from all of the great attractions sarasota has to offer. Schedule your showing today!
